### Trigger Travel Assistant — flights and hotels (multi-destination)
POST http://localhost:8001/agent/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "task": "Find me flights and hotels to London and Amsterdam"
}

### Trigger Travel Assistant — flights and hotels (single destination)
POST http://localhost:8001/agent/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "task": "Find me flights and hotels to London"
}

### Trigger Travel Assistant — flights only
POST http://localhost:8001/agent/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "task": "Find me only flights to London and Amsterdam"
}
